tspan.tspan: I like this product but I don't think it's for me. I usually have oily skin and it can make me feel a little greasy when layered with moisturizer.
I haven't used it with makeup at all, I think that wearing a light foundation over the top will give an excellent glow. The benefits are still
definite (I think - lol I just SPLURGED on skincare products so my skin will be getting all of those benefits too) I have decided to only
use this in the AM every 2 days or so and I only use about half a pump instead of a full pump.

text.data-name: Average Not bad not great. It’s good under makeup but it doesn’t seem to do anything great for my skin.
